INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `image_path`, `user_id`, `product_id`, `course_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `subtitle`, `content`, `tag_id`, `like_count`, `is_deleted`, `created_at`, `update_time`) VALUES
(1, 'https://media.vogue.com.tw/photos/678cd28a6c7849351720e07c/2:3/w_1920,c_limit/18_Lobby%20View%201%20with%20Base.png', 48, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Nikon 正在開發 Nikon Z 接環系統適用的 NIKKOR Z 28-135mm f/4 PZ 標準變焦鏡頭', 'GOOD', '<h2><strong>專為影片創作者而生的電動變焦鏡頭</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\"https://www.coolpix.com.tw/cruis_work/upload_file/htmlimages_new/1730275592.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p><p>*實際產品外型或與以上圖片所示不同。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>日本 Nikon 隆重宣佈正在全力開發 NIKKOR Z 28-135mm f/4 PZ 標準變焦鏡頭，相容採用 Nikon Z 接環的全片幅/FX 格式無反相機。</p><p>NIKKOR Z 28-135mm f/4 PZ 電動變焦鏡頭涵蓋 28mm 至 135mm 焦距範圍，開發目標以影片拍攝為主，操作便捷且具備卓越光學性能，能有效支援個人攝影師或小型團隊進行紀錄片或外景拍攝。</p><p>Nikon 致力拓展光學科技的嶄新領域，貼近用戶需求，持續發展影像文化，期望開發影像表達的無限可能！</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>關於 NIKKOR 品牌</strong></p><p>NIKKOR 是 Nikon 旗下的攝影鏡頭品牌，NIKKOR 的名稱來自「NIKKO」一字加「R」結尾而成，是當時業界普遍為攝影鏡頭命名的方法，而「Nikko」就是 Nikon 公司本名「日本光學工業」的羅馬拼音縮寫。2024 年 4 月，Nikon 宣佈可換鏡頭相機專用的 NIKKOR 鏡頭總生產量已達 1.2 億支，為 Nikon 的成就紀錄再次寫下里程碑。於 2023 年 11 月，Nikon 慶祝 NIKKOR 成立 90 週年；時至今日，NIKKOR 已經是國際公認的品牌，同時亦不斷突破攝影界限，超越所想。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>關於 NIKON</strong></p><p>Nikon 是數位影像、精密光學和攝影技術方面的全球領導者，其獲獎無數的消費型和專業攝影設備為產品設計和性能奠定嶄新標準，並廣受世界認可。Nikon 在 50 多個國家/地區中經銷消費型和專業的數位單眼相機、NIKKOR 光學產品、閃光燈和系統配件、Nikon COOLPIX 輕便型數位相機、Nikon 運動鏡頭，以及最新無反光鏡相機。</p><p>如欲了解詳情，請瀏覽 <a href=\"https://www.nikon.com.tw/\">https://www.nikon.com.tw</a> 或探索 Z 系列無反光鏡相機系統，並體驗嶄新創作的無限潛能：<a href=\"https://coolpix.com.tw/shop/%E7%84%A1%E5%8F%8D%E5%85%89%E9%8F%A1%E7%9B%B8%E6%A9%9F\">https://coolpix.com.tw/shop/無反光鏡相機</a> 。</p><p>亦歡迎瀏覽 Nikon Facebook <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NikonTaiwan\">www.facebook.com/NikonTaiwan</a> 、Instagram <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/Nikon_Taiwan\">www.instagram.com/Nikon_Taiwan</a> 及 YouTube <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@NikonTaiwan\">www.youtube.com/@NikonTaiwan</a> 頻道，與 Nikon 及其他攝影師交流。</p>', NULL, 85, 0, '2024-11-12 13:25:24', '2025-02-12 13:25:24'),
(2, 'https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f608443ed5430006718b31', 48, NULL, NULL, 2, '攝影入門必學：3 種常見的「焦段」與「視角」的變化', '如何控制景深，以及相機、被攝者、背景之間的距離比例，絕對是在使用望遠鏡頭拍攝時，會需要注意的事項，Hahow 邀請張道慈老師來分享 3 種攝影入門必學的焦段及視角變化！', '<p data-nodeid=\"155\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">即便是只使用手機做日常的拍攝，也會對「zoom in」這個動作有些許的概念，在手機螢幕上滑動雙指，放大以及縮小畫面，是一件很自然的行為。</p><p data-nodeid=\"156\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>在攝影上，這樣單純的 「zoom in」，背後牽扯到一個很重要的觀念就是「焦段」。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"157\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>3 種攝影常用的不同焦段與效果</h2><p data-nodeid=\"158\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>市面上的鏡頭分為兩大類，一類是「定焦鏡」，也就是無法放大、縮小的那種。另一類是「變焦鏡」，就是可以讓你轉動變焦環，來達到拉遠、拉近的效果。</p><p data-nodeid=\"159\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>為了說明簡單，我們很粗淺地把焦段分成三大類，由數字少到數字多，分別是「廣角」、「標準」、「望遠」三個區塊，當你注意到在購買鏡頭時，一定會有一個你無法忽視的參數就是「焦段」，你要購買哪種焦段的鏡頭，間接的也影響了你的拍攝內容。</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"160\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>標準焦段</h3><p data-nodeid=\"161\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>先從「標準」說起，一般來說在 50mm 上下，我們會稱呼其為標準焦段鏡頭，往下也許到 40mm 還勉強，往上可能不超過 85mm。</p><p data-nodeid=\"162\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"207\" alt=\"標準焦段\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f608443ed5430006718b31\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：張道慈老師提供</p><p data-nodeid=\"163\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>這樣的焦段，很容易可以拍到人物帶景，要拍攝任何日常的畫面都很合適，尤其對於比較不喜歡鏡頭「變形」的人來說，標準鏡頭在入門的構圖上，相較於廣角鏡來說可能會更簡單一些。</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"164\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>廣角焦段</h3><p data-nodeid=\"165\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>接著是「廣角」鏡，當焦段小於 35mm 後，就會歸類在廣角鏡，而如果更廣，例如 16mm 甚至數字更小，也會被稱為「超廣角」，再往下就會進入「魚眼」的世界。</p><p data-nodeid=\"166\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>廣角端在拍攝時，有兩個比較需要留意的地方：「變形」以及「深景深」，廣角鏡頭的形變量大，景深較深，這點無論在拍攝什麼題材，都會是特別需要注意的。</p><p data-nodeid=\"167\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"216\" alt=\"廣角焦段\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f608b9d496bc0007b59e4a\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：張道慈老師提供</p><p data-nodeid=\"168\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>即便我把光圈開的很大，對焦在後面的房屋上，但前面的鐵柵欄依然是看得出形體的，這就是景深很深時的優點，當然，對於想要追求散景的人來說，廣角端就不如望遠鏡頭那麼討喜了。</p><p data-nodeid=\"169\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"222\" alt=\"廣角焦段 2\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f608d4d496bc0007b5a614\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：張道慈老師提供</p><p data-nodeid=\"170\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>廣角鏡頭會有明顯的形變，當然換個說法，也可以稱呼其為「張力」，張力運用得當，可以讓照片有與標準鏡頭很不同的感覺，但如果沒有控制好水平線，也可能會讓畫面過於歪斜，造成觀賞者觀看時的不適感。</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"171\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>望遠焦段</h3><p data-nodeid=\"172\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>而望遠鏡頭，乍看之下畫面較為平穩，這點與標準鏡頭似乎比較類似，但隨著焦段越長，視角越窄，跟廣角一樣，有兩個主要的特色 - 「壓縮感」以及「淺景深」</p><p data-nodeid=\"173\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"230\" alt=\"望遠焦段\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f608f23ed543000671d35d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：張道慈老師提供</p><p data-nodeid=\"174\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>越望遠的焦段，所呈現出的壓縮感就越強，以上面雪梨歌劇院的照片來看，後方的雪梨大橋幾乎要跟歌劇院黏在一起了，這樣把 3D 的畫面轉成 2D 平面的感覺，就來自於「壓縮感」。</p><p data-nodeid=\"175\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"236\" alt=\"望遠焦段2\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f609061307110006c467f4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：張道慈老師提供</p><p data-nodeid=\"176\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>而較淺的景深也是望遠鏡頭的特色，當鏡頭與主體的距離，遠小於主體與背景的距離時，淺景深的感覺會非常明顯，優勢是可以把混亂的背景變成散景，在拍攝上，也會較有夢幻的感覺。缺點就是那句老話，一不小心就把巴黎拍成八里。</p><p data-nodeid=\"177\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>如何去控制景深，以及相機、被攝者、背景之間的距離比例，絕對是在使用望遠鏡頭拍攝時，會需要注意的事項。</p>', NULL, 165, 0, '2024-11-17 00:02:38', '2025-02-17 00:02:38'),
(3, 'https://images.api.hahow.in/images/63048bdc11b7f60007f0415e', 12, NULL, NULL, 2, '輕鬆施展讓照片變美麗的魔法——三個關於質感濾鏡的實用技巧', '濾鏡幾乎是現代人手必備的魔法秘寶，但同樣的濾鏡，有些人用的得心應手，但有些人卻不知從何下手。該怎麼應用濾鏡表現出自己想要的畫面呢？就讓 Hahow 來告訴你吧！', '<h2 data-nodeid=\"1818\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">技巧一、找到專屬自己的那根魔法棒&mdash;&mdash;實用又豐富的濾鏡 APP</h2><p data-nodeid=\"1819\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>濾鏡的種類多樣，就跟每個人的穿搭都會不同一樣，每張照片適合的濾鏡也會有所不同。以下有幾款懶人濾鏡 APP，適合每日不同心情的你喔！</p><p data-nodeid=\"1820\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"1867\" alt=\"質感濾鏡的實用技巧\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/63048bdc11b7f60007f0415e\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：Hahow 圖庫</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"1821\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Snow</h3><p data-nodeid=\"1822\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Snow 以擁有許多可愛的 AR 自拍濾鏡為名，人臉識別的能力很好，就算是三個人一起出現在鏡頭裡，也可以快速抓住五官。濾鏡多半以日常風為主，低飽和自然，適合搭配背景，營造出門的悠閒感。</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"1823\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Tezza</h3><p data-nodeid=\"1824\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Tezza 是被許多專業 IG 經營者使用的 App，比較主要的功能有三種，一是照片編輯，可以用來套濾鏡、加字幕等；二是模版編輯，Tezza 本身就有很多內建版面，可以用來製作多圖版面；三就是濾鏡本身，多數的濾鏡比較偏向韓系低彩，對比較低。不過 Tezza 的進階功能是要付費的，可以依需求再進行購買。</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"1825\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Foodie</h3><p data-nodeid=\"1826\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Foodie 是一款提供食物濾鏡的 APP，擁有清晰好分辨的標籤，例如肉、蛋糕等，可以依照拍攝的內容來選擇。另外也提供像是「絕佳角度」或「柔焦」之類的功能，絕佳角度可以讓用戶透過顏色提醒，擺放鏡頭讓照片看起來像是美食雜誌上的食物；而柔焦則讓影像有類似單眼相機一樣的氛圍質感，還有亮度調節以及閃光燈等功能。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"1827\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>技巧二、把擾人因素變不見的小妙招&mdash;&mdash;能夠巧妙遮蔽缺陷的拍照 APP</h2><p data-nodeid=\"1828\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>有些人會說，拍出好照片是需要天時、地利、人和的。但事實是我們有時候並不能控制一些外在的干擾因素，比如說在景點後方走動的路人、陰沉的天氣等。不過或許你會想，那為什麼有些人拍出來的照片總是特別漂亮呢？是不是有什麼技巧？</p><p data-nodeid=\"1829\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>這是當然的，而在使用以下幾款拍照 APP 後，你也可以簡單拍出美麗照片喔！</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"1830\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>打造天時&mdash;&mdash; PICNIC</h3><p data-nodeid=\"1831\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>PICNIC 是一款可以幫助人們打造美麗背景的 APP，無論是在都市拍照時容易遇到的微塵，還是在好不容易出門旅遊時遇到採光不理想的陰天，只要開啟 PICNIC 特效，無論是晴天、晚霞、星空，都可以輕鬆拍出理想好天氣！</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"1832\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>製造地利&mdash;&mdash; Snapseed</h3><p data-nodeid=\"1833\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Snapseed 是一款專業的修圖 APP，而其中的自動雜點修復能夠輕鬆地去除拍照時背景的多於物體。而 Snapseed 的操作也非常簡單，只要在想要抹除的人物上輕輕滑過，在就會自動完成接下來的動作。而且 Snapseed 也會按照四周的環境景物來修復抹除部分，效果自然，能夠輕鬆解決遇到躲避路人的困擾。</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"1834\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>營造人和&mdash;&mdash; ZopeZope</h3><p data-nodeid=\"1835\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>在旅行途中，拍照製造回憶是許多拍攝愛好者會做的事，但如果是因為同行者不善於擺姿勢，而導致遲遲拍不出照片怎麼辦？ZopeZope 是一款專門為了多人拍攝而打造的 APP，其中提供了許多姿勢可以對照拍攝，就算是不擅長擺姿勢的旅伴，也可以依 APP 的姿勢導引，拍出美麗照片喔！</p><p data-nodeid=\"1836\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"1887\" alt=\"質感濾鏡的實用技巧\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/63048b9504a8a800065b410a\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：Hahow 圖庫</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"1837\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>技巧三、想要屬於自己的獨一無二美魔法？進階打造專屬濾鏡的專業 APP &mdash;&mdash; Lightroom</h2><p data-nodeid=\"1838\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Adobe Photoshop Lightroom 是一款專業的修圖 APP，擁有非常強大的修圖功能，可以利用調色數據來打造出符合自己預想風格的濾鏡。如果你覺得上述濾鏡 APP 雖然方便，但卻不那麼適合自己的話，那 Lightroom 會是個能夠讓你量身打造理想濾鏡的選擇。</p><p data-nodeid=\"1839\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>包括調整雜訊、敏銳化和顆粒化相片、重建強光和陰影，帶出細節等，都能夠利用 Lightroom 做到。而 Lightroom 對於習慣將照片打印、沖洗出來的用戶也十分友善，如果你有收藏實體相片的習慣，Lightroom 也提供在修圖後可以預先檢視打印後的色彩，讓用戶可以提早調整色差，避免打印後才發現照片不如預期。</p><p data-nodeid=\"1840\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>如果想要讓照片看起來更美，可以考慮先從最基礎的加強陰影、對比開始做起，接著再進行調色。網路上有許多公開的熱門 Lightroom 調色數據，如果是對於色彩不熟悉的用戶，在其中找出自己喜歡的調色方向，複製數據再稍加修改，也不失為一種辦法喔！</p><p data-nodeid=\"1841\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"1896\" alt=\"質感濾鏡的實用技巧\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/63048bbaf24bb30006113309\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：Hahow 圖庫</p><p data-nodeid=\"1842\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>在看過以上三個技巧過後，你是否也想試試對自己的照片施展美麗魔法了呢？想要像網美們一樣拍出好照片其實很簡單！只要用對技巧，學會利用工具的輔助，製造屬於自己的風景，你也可以擁有美麗而獨樹一幟的照片風格喔！快來一起試試看吧！</p>', NULL, 326, 0, '2024-11-17 01:50:51', '2025-02-17 01:50:51');
