ransparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>2. 側面拍照角度：相機鏡頭在被拍攝對象正側面90度拍攝</h3><p data-nodeid=\"2645\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>交代動作方向及事物之間的方向聯繫，展現輪廓特徵，適合表現動作姿態。</p><p data-nodeid=\"2646\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"2719\" alt=\"攝影技巧\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/636b1c23061591bfad51aeed\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：韓森影像 提供</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"2647\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: no