p: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>4. 背面拍照角度：相機在被拍攝對象的後面進行拍攝</h3><p data-nodeid=\"2651\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>這樣的角度觀眾的帶入感會很強烈，適合製造懸念，給人想像空間。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"2652\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>拍照技巧關鍵之二：「拍攝高度」</h2><h3 data-nodeid=\"2653\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: nor