ii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：韓森影像 提供</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"2659\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>3. 低角度拍攝技巧：鏡頭比被拍攝對象更高</h3><p data-nodeid=\"2660\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>適合遠距離拍攝大場面，表現畫面中線條的縱深感，拍人像時稍微俯角也會讓被攝者臉顯得更小喔！</p><p data-nodeid=\"2661\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"2760\" alt=\"攝影技巧\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/636b23fd7bd3fc22f3bc6d63\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：韓森影像 提供</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"2662\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>4. 頂角度拍攝技巧：相機從上往下垂直拍攝物體，鏡頭與地面成平行</h3><p data-nodeid=\"2663\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>常見於空拍機，或是日常的拍攝食物及商品等等，因為能讓原本立體的被攝物形成一圈一圈的圖案美感，也是一種簡化畫面的方法喔。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"2664\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>拍照技巧關鍵之三：「拍攝距離」</h2><h3 data-nodeid=\"2665\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>1. 遠景攝影技巧：在距離主體較遠的地方進行拍攝</h3><p data-nodeid=\"2666\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>拍攝地平面時，避免畫面中的線條切割主體，至少盡量不要切頭，也可以適當的配合前景讓畫面更有立體感。</p><p data-nodeid=\"2667\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"2774\" alt=\"攝影技巧\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/636b240e7bd3fce39bbc75aa\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：韓森影像 提供</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"2668\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>2. 全景攝影技巧：拍攝主體全部</h3><p data-nodeid=\"2669\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>展現被拍攝物體全貌，呈現主角與四周環境的關係，但是要注意畫面的簡潔度，畫面範圍入鏡越多，就相對容易把不必要的元素一起拍進去。</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"2670\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>3. 中景攝影技巧：拍攝物體主體 3/4</h3><p data-nodeid=\"2671\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>拍攝物體主體的絕大部分，拍攝站立中的人物，取景大約是在膝蓋以上，拍坐著的人大約就是拍攝腰部及以上的範圍。</p><p data-nodeid=\"2672\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"2787\" alt=\"攝影技巧\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/636b2423e701e8c3e7013ffa\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：韓森影像 提供</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"2673\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>4. 近景攝影技巧：拍攝人物胸部及以上</h3><p data-nodeid=\"2674\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>用來細緻地表現人物的臉部神態和情緒，適合用於刻畫人物性格。</p><p data-nodeid=\"2675\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"2796\" alt=\"攝影技巧\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/636b2433a527490b76fb0ab9\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：韓森影像 提供</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"2676\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>5. 特寫攝影技巧：只拍攝人物的某個局部</h3><p data-nodeid=\"2677\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>例如只有唇、或眼睛，這種特寫可以充分表現人物富有意義或情緒的局部擷取，常用於放大形象、強化內容、突出細節等效果，可以為你的攝影作品帶來一種預期和探索的氛圍喔。</p><p data-nodeid=\"2678\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"2805\" alt=\"攝影技巧\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/636241a267f2d500605a8b33\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：韓森影像 提供</p>', NULL, 125, 0, '2025-01-17 02:45:36', '2025-02-17 02:45:36'),
(8, 'https://media.vogue.com.tw/photos/6772636ece2df6bc69a1ecbf/3:2/w_1280,c_limit/HH7_0911.jpg', 33, NULL, NULL, 2, '攝影入門必學：轉換色溫與白平衡所延伸的情緒詮釋', '「色溫」與「白平衡」這兩個名詞看似是在講一樣的事情，但其實本質上是完全不同的，但對於新手來說，這的確是個時常會搞混的名詞。Hahow 邀請張道慈老師分享不同色溫與白平衡的實際應用。', '<h2 data-nodeid=\"2965\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">色溫是什麼？色溫可以創造什麼效果？</h2><p data-nodeid=\"2966\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>「色溫」是自然的現象，太陽的光線是全部的可見光，有全部的顏色（白色），當太陽沒入地表，夕陽西下時（或是剛日出的時候，但因為多數人對夕陽比較有印象，所以後面全部都以夕陽為例），因為大氣層折射的關係，我們會先看到紅色、橘色，一瞬間可能有機會看到綠色，最後就是偏藍色的冷色溫。</p><p data-nodeid=\"2967\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>如果想要知道更多關於色溫的物理原理，可以自行 google 科普一下，這邊就不講太多，這是聊攝影不是聊科學。總之如果把白平衡都設定成 5500k （白光色溫），那白天的照片白色就是白色，然後傍晚就開始變暖色，最後變冷色。</p><p data-nodeid=\"2968\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"3002\" alt=\"攝影必學入門1\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f616880e1adc000640d9d9\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：張道慈老師提供</p><p data-nodeid=\"2969\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"3007\" alt=\"攝影必學入門2\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f616b5d496bc0007ba52b3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：張道慈老師提供</p><p data-nodeid=\"2970\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"3012\" alt=\"攝影必學入門3\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f616c51307110006c913ec\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：張道慈老師提供</p><p data-nodeid=\"2971\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>這是正常，肉眼也可以感受到的部分，也就是色溫的變化。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"2972\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>白平衡是什麼？白平衡的功能為何？</h2><p data-nodeid=\"2973\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>那白平衡的功能是什麼呢？無論是在室外或是室內，隨著燈光的變化，環境中會有不同的色溫，但如果我們想把這些「偏暖」或「偏冷」的色溫造成畫面顏色的變化「修正」成白光下看到的樣子，就要透過「白平衡」來做修正。</p><p data-nodeid=\"2974\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>是的，所謂的「白平衡」其實就是一個數位修正色溫的功能。由於現在有許多朋友也開始回頭玩底片相機，過去在底片時代，則是會利用不同的底片，或是透過濾鏡來控制白平衡，這也是一個數位時代很便利的功能。</p><p data-nodeid=\"2975\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>而對我來說，影像的色溫調整並不是在追求「正確」，並不是把一張照片的白色都修正成白色才是正確的照片，依照我們要給照片的情緒，利用暖色跟冷色可以給照片不同的情緒。</p><p data-nodeid=\"2976\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>如果你總是將白平衡設定成自動，下次可以試試看調整不同 k 值，感受一下不同 k 值在環境下帶來的變化，可能會對於影像的詮釋上有不同的想法。</p>', NULL, 154, 0, '2025-01-17 02:49:55', '2025-02-17 02:49:55');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `image_path`, `user_id`, `product_id`, `course_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `subtitle`, `content`, `tag_id`, `like_count`, `is_deleted`, `created_at`, `update_time`) VALUES
(9, 'https://media.vogue.com.tw/photos/67a493df65855c12fbc2f243/2:3/w_1280,c_limit/Snapinst.app_439985052_806828384657458_3015723514527082312_n_1080.jpg', 17, NULL, NULL, 3, '藝術攝影師章潔——生活即是靈感所在，好與壞都將透過觀景窗顯影出來', '晚上十點，通常是世界開始慢慢安靜下來的時刻；而地球的另一端恰好相反，正是城市進入喧鬧之時。我與章潔隔著 12 小時的時差，聊學習、也聊創作，有趣的是，每段對話最後都繞回「關於自我」的課題。', '<p data-nodeid=\"3236\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">為了了解自己真正的樣子，我們可能會做各種嘗試摸索自己的極限，找出真正喜歡、在意的事物；又或者進行夢境分析，看看我們究竟藏了什麼在潛意識裡。然而，人永遠無法追上自己變化的速度，所以上述兩件事永遠無法做到滿分。</p><p data-nodeid=\"3237\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>因此章潔追求的並不是結果，而是探索的過程。她用各種方式分析自己，並將概念視覺化，成為一幅又一幅的作品，就像一場永無止盡的實驗，只是沒有成功或失敗的結論，只有不斷嘗試創新與調整方式的動態過程。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"3238\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>每幅作品都蘊含創作者的一克靈魂</h2><p data-nodeid=\"3239\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"3304\" alt=\"章潔1\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f2060f069c6a0006cd28d5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：Hahow 圖庫</p><p data-nodeid=\"3240\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>從事和創作有關的工作，常常都會面臨一個困擾&mdash;&mdash;靈感從哪裡來？畢竟不是天天都在上演電影情節，即便原有的素材再多，也有用盡的一天，如何不讓自己每天追著靈感跑，章潔摸索出一套自己的邏輯。</p><p data-nodeid=\"3241\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>首先，一定要詢問自己，創作的目的是什麼？不論是單純地記錄生活、想要講述某個故事或觀點，甚至是做一些在現實中做不到的事。作品之所以會有靈魂，是因為它匯集了創作者的過往經歷、遇到的人事物以及透過學習得到的收穫，知道自己為何創作，才能讓作品不只是流於追求形式，漸漸發展出自己的風格。當然，剛入門時，難免會透過「模仿」來摸索，但需謹記在心的是，可以學習他人的技法，但要以此為立基點再加以延伸，如果只是一味地複製，沒有加入自己的想法，即便模仿得再像，終究只是沒有靈魂的仿製品。</p><p data-nodeid=\"3242\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>對於尚在摸索自己風格的讀者，章潔建議可以先觀察及研究自己所關注的創作者，這個對象可以是自己欣賞的，也可以是與自身喜好大相徑庭的。選定之後，針對以下三個方向進行分析：</p><ul data-nodeid=\"3243\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li data-nodeid=\"3244\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p data-nodeid=\"3245\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\">視覺呈現：像是畫面組成、色彩配置、構圖、技巧等。</p></li><li data-nodeid=\"3246\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p data-nodeid=\"3247\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\">創作動機：創作者想要傳達什麼故事？在什麼樣的創作背景下，產生這樣的想法？</p></li><li data-nodeid=\"3248\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p data-nodeid=\"3249\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\">行銷手法：創作者要如何行銷自己，獲得關注？包含研究作品的藝術價值、創作者在產業中的 地位等，也就是要探討案例成功的原因。</p></li></ul><h2 data-nodeid=\"3250\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>白天曝光，晚上顯影</h2><p data-nodeid=\"3251\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>不同於創作或工作時，一定得清楚自己的「目的」為何，平常的靈感累積更像是要讓自己無意地接收訊息。章潔的創作養分大多來自於生活經驗，她曾學過繪畫、當過 dancer，這兩項元素分別在《City Illusion》及《Self Portrait》系列中展露無遺，前者主要在視覺呈現上帶有繪畫的筆觸質感，後者則表現在鮮豔色彩及肢體展現上。</p><p data-nodeid=\"3252\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"3317\" alt=\"章潔2\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f2080f5df01100073fac84\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：Hahow 圖庫</p><p data-nodeid=\"3253\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>現在的她除了觀看電影及藝術家的作品集（*註1）外，她還很常與不同領域的人聊天。她認為若是太常待在同個領域或環境裡，思想及眼界容易被侷限，在聆聽不同故事的過程中，有些可能會直接地和自己原先的東西產生火花，有些則是間接地，像是透過某個關鍵字，刺激自己思考，聯想到其他的可能。</p><blockquote data-nodeid=\"3254\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 17.5px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 190, 164); border-top-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-right-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><p data-nodeid=\"3255\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><em data-nodeid=\"3326\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">「生命裡最難的不是一直跳脫現有環境、適應新的地方；最難且最需要勇氣的是，在你原本適應、熟悉的日常中待下來，然後慢慢地去習慣每天會遇到的挑戰。」</em></p></blockquote><p data-nodeid=\"3256\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>有時，她會走上街，沒有規劃任何目的地，就只是單純地感受城市的面貌、文化與故事，累了就找家咖啡廳，坐在窗邊觀察路人的肢體、表情，猜想他們之間的關係是什麼？相處模式又是什麼？這對長期旅居在外的章潔來說，是很重要的生活練習，尤其她時常處於移動中的狀態，每當搭乘長期的火車或飛機，就是她和自己相處的最佳時刻，透過自我對話，往往也讓她產生許多想法。</p><p data-nodeid=\"3257\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>她每日的作息就像是底片攝影的過程。</p><p data-nodeid=\"3258\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"3331\" alt=\"章潔3\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f208345df01100073fb88d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：Hahow 圖庫</p><p data-nodeid=\"3259\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>白天曝光自己，接收所有舊的、新的、熟悉的、陌生的等等各種複雜的資訊；晚上則回到暗房，慢慢沖洗白天接收到的訊息。有些經過消化、沉澱後，顯影在照片上；有些則因為曝光不足，消失在影像中。但無須過於在意成品是好是壞，重要的是你願意享受一個人待在暗房的孤獨感，並將它沖洗出來，若總是不整理、將它們放置在一旁，仍就只是一捲捲的底片，最後隨著時間過了期，便再也顯影不出影像。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"3260\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>創作是為了探索自己的本質</h2><p data-nodeid=\"3261\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>從章潔身上深刻體悟到創作必須由自身出發，才能賦予作品靈魂。在採訪尾聲，我請章潔以自己為題，想像一下她會如何呈現這幅作品。她先是沉思一會，才緩緩地開口描述，她腦中浮現的影像上有著自己身形的輪廓，裡面疊滿了過往的生活片刻。若是靠近觀看，會清楚地知道這是哪個時刻、發生了什麼事；但若只是站遠處，便只會看到一團將各種色彩揉合之後的不那麼飽和、帶點神秘感的黑色。</p><p data-nodeid=\"3262\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"3339\" alt=\"章潔4\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/62f2084ed496bc000753788b\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">圖片來源：Hahow 圖庫</p><p data-nodeid=\"3263\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>她進一步地解釋道，「章潔」就是由細碎的生活片段與細節所組成，因為認真活在當下，每一刻都珍貴，不論是好、是壞都能化作養分，成為創作的靈感來源。身為創作者最需要做的一件事就是好好生活，為自己保留充電與沉澱的時間，勇敢地向內心深處挖掘，唯有不斷地練習自我覺察，才能越來越接近自己真正想要的核心價值。</p><p data-nodeid=\"3264\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>當清楚地明白自己為何而創作，即便外人不懂那一團黑所代表的意義也沒關係了，這是她與世界的秘密&mdash;&mdash;將自己全然交出去，用最真實的自己與世界碰撞，只為了那一閃而逝的火花。</p><p data-nodeid=\"3265\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>推薦你，跟著章潔一起在 Hahow 探索生活的本質：</p><h3 data-nodeid=\"3266\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.8rem; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>▶&nbsp;<a data-nodeid=\"3348\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://localhost:3000/course\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 190, 164); text-decoration: underline; cursor: pointer; outline: none;\">【影像說書人】攝影不只是按下快門</a></h3><p data-nodeid=\"3267\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">註1：<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">章潔推薦的電影及藝術家作品集：</p><ol data-nodeid=\"3268\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li data-nodeid=\"3269\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p data-nodeid=\"3270\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\">《奇風歲月（Boy&rsquo;s Life）》：用童年角度講述主角的經歷，每個故事都對往後的人生有所啟發，能夠讓人重新感受自己的初衷。</p></li><li data-nodeid=\"3271\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p data-nodeid=\"3272\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\">《大智若魚（Big Fish）》：用帶有童話、寓言的方式講述故事。</p></li><li data-nodeid=\"3273\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p data-nodeid=\"3274\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\">《Before》系列三部曲：藉由對話的方式感受人生的轉變。</p></li><li data-nodeid=\"3275\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p data-nodeid=\"3276\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\">杉本博司的作品集：作品中帶有建築、哲學概念，能夠從中感受到不同領域的碰撞。</p></li><li data-nodeid=\"3277\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><p data-nodeid=\"3278\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em;\">蘇菲卡爾的作品集：擅長概念、實驗式的行為藝術，知名作品為《極度疼痛》。</p></li></ol>', NULL, 27, 0, '2025-01-17 02:53:06', '2025-02-17 02:53:06'),
(10, 'https://media.vogue.com.tw/photos/67af281e5c6682629d6382dd/2:3/w_2240,c_limit/SaraSakanaka%E2%80%9440%20(1).jpg', 22, NULL, NULL, 4, '時尚攝影師凡寧：在攝影和書寫裡，一字一幕建構出自己的雙城故事', '第一次見到凡寧本人時，覺得她略有距離感，細聊後才發現，那或許是她習慣保護自己的一種方式，小心翼翼地不讓人察覺自己的不安全感，選擇將情緒蜷收，讓人難以一眼看穿她的真實想法，得亦步亦趨地、有耐心地慢慢靠近，才有機會一探凡寧的人生故事。', '<p data-nodeid=\"4822\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">在成為運用影像和文字傳遞訊息的時尚工作者前，她曾是薪資優渥的空間設計師，有著令人稱羨的亮麗生活。二十六歲那年，緣分讓她遇上了現在的先生，毅然決然地決定遠赴德國。乍聽之下是個浪漫至極的童話故事，但現實中有太多層面需要考量，大量的挑戰及挫折便隨著為愛走天涯這個決定後接踵而來。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"4823\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>初至德國，按下歸零鍵重整人生</h2><p data-nodeid=\"4824\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>來到人生地不熟的第三語言國家，首當其衝的便是語言，不僅原有的人脈、工作成就歸零，就連最基本的溝通都得重新學習。</p><blockquote data-nodeid=\"4825\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 17.5px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 190, 164); border-top-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-right-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><p data-nodeid=\"4826\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.75em;\">「我身旁大部分的德國人即便有英文能力，也沒有和我這個德文初學者以英文溝通。」</p></blockquote><p data-nodeid=\"4827\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>凡寧談到出席家庭或朋友聚會時，常常大家笑成一團，自己卻不懂笑點在哪，無法即時地給出反應，也不可能請另一半逐步翻譯，因此生活時常籠罩著強烈的不安全感。</p><p data-nodeid=\"4828\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>加上先生當時與其前任尚處在離婚階段（＊備註一），兩人時常為了前家庭的話題出現爭執，語言及愛情的進展都時常偏離軌道。兩年後，凡寧懷孕了，沒有工作的她只能待在家中，各種情緒交織在一起，讓她感到心力交瘁，時常質疑自己是個「魯蛇」。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"4829\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>放晴的天氣預報，融化她心底堆積如山的積雪</h2><p data-nodeid=\"4830\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>是否想過做些什麼改變這樣的情形？凡寧輕輕地搖頭，「當時我所面臨的困境就像緊緊纏繞的死結，即使自己拼命對於渴望掌握事物的她，面對自己無法掌控的情況，感到十分地焦躁不安，也曾萌生想逃離的念頭，但這樣消極的想法只停留了幾秒鐘，因為凡寧知道自己唯一的路只有一路向前。「因為有了孩子，而且已經全然拋下台灣的生活，對我來說沒有退路，只好硬著頭皮往前走。」<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"4883\" alt=\"攝影師 凡寧\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/66728d8c0638c9d39cddb20c\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></p><p data-nodeid=\"4831\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>看似無解的難題，在她待在德國的第四年有了變化。某天，她點開車上的廣播，發現自己竟聽懂了天氣預報的內容，瞬間淚水充滿眼眶，一路哭著回家。</p><blockquote data-nodeid=\"4832\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 17.5px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 190, 164); border-top-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-right-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><p data-nodeid=\"4833\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.75em;\">「因為語言不可能是昨天到明天（突然就學會），那是不是代表我過去幾年已經累積了基本的聽力能力，只是我一直沒有察覺？」</p></blockquote><p data-nodeid=\"4834\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>凡寧憶起當時的情景，依然語帶激動，就像在最脆弱、懷疑自己的時候，有人拍拍自己的肩膀，告訴自己或許進步的速度有些緩慢，但終究有在往前走。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"4835\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>成功是 1% 的天份，加上 99% 的努力</h2><p data-nodeid=\"4836\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>差不多在同一時期，凡寧開始拿起相機。當時社群平台不多，就連 Facebook 也才剛開始，更不用談線上的學習平台。因此，她練習的方式就是多看、多拍，遇到欣賞的照片，便試著利用 Google 關鍵字搜尋，了解技巧原理後，再自己嘗試創作。</p><p data-nodeid=\"4837\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>近年，她偏愛使用 Pinterest 作為搜集資料及靈感的管道，由於 Pinterest 提供用戶按主題分類，可以添加及管理自己的圖片收藏，對於從事視覺設計相關的工作者來說相當方便。另外，她也喜歡訂閱攝影師的電子報，透過這些免費資源來學習。</p><p data-nodeid=\"4838\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>多年累積下來，凡寧已經整理出自己的一套心法，她認為「學習技巧」只是第一步，要如何把學到的東西整理成有脈絡的分析，分享給其他人，才是接著要去思考的重要議題，這也正是她想成立「<a data-nodeid=\"4895\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://yespleaseenjoy.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 190, 164); text-decoration: underline; cursor: pointer; outline: none;\">Yes! Please Enjoy</a>」的初衷。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"4900\" alt=\"攝影師 凡寧\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/66728da275e58cf0bb403fc4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></p><blockquote data-nodeid=\"4839\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 17.5px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 190, 164); border-top-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-right-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><p data-nodeid=\"4840\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.75em;\">「華人吃東西前，習慣說『慢慢吃』、『請慢用』，朋友來到我們家裡就會說『Enjoy!』、『Don&rsquo;t be shy.』，那是一個打開心房的招呼語。這也提醒我，必須要先打開自己的心房，才能讓邀請來的人享受自己準備的東西（內容）；另一點是，必須要慢慢地品味生活中的狀況，因為慢下來，才不會錯過人與人之間或人與環境之間一些很重要的情緒互動。」&mdash;&mdash; 凡寧</p></blockquote><h2 data-nodeid=\"4841\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>路是人走出來的，機會得用雙手緊緊握住</h2><p data-nodeid=\"4842\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>除了拍照，她也開始提筆寫下自己的觀點，甚至思考如何將「影像」及「文字」做得更深入。在先生與前任終於完成法律上的離婚程序後，隨之而來的贍養費與家庭支出，構成了她生活中的另一道難題。拿起相機後的凡寧不再是那個初到德國的「魯蛇」，反而更努力地尋找各種可能的收入來源，為的是過著自己理想中的生活樣態。</p><blockquote data-nodeid=\"4843\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 17.5px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 190, 164); border-top-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-right-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><p data-nodeid=\"4844\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.75em;\">「現實的求生欲，讓我必須要動腦筋去找到收入來源，有任何機會就要把握。」</p></blockquote><p data-nodeid=\"4845\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>她開始積極地聯繫台灣的編輯，與幾家媒體平台合作專欄。同時，為了增進自己的攝影能力，花了約三、四年的時間訓練自己，四處幫人免費拍照。有次，她幫女兒的幼稚園老師拍了懷孕寫真，對方看了很喜歡，在孩子出生後，再度找了凡寧拍攝，並付了第一筆拍攝費用，就連聖誕節要拍的全家福照，也指定由凡寧掌鏡。過去的免費拍攝經驗，讓她累積了大量的作品，加上被攝者的口耳相傳，讓她開始慢慢地有了收入。</p><p data-nodeid=\"4846\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>2012 年，社群媒體剛開始蓬勃發展，她察覺到時尚圈在德國正要起飛，由於過去曾待在設計領域，恰巧是她可以發揮之處，於是積極地與案主聯繫，進而接觸到德國的時尚編輯，開始看秀、做設計師專訪，並與相關品牌合作。</p><h2 data-nodeid=\"4847\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 20px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>在攝影裡找到歸屬感，建構出凡寧獨特的雙城故事</h2><p data-nodeid=\"4848\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>回首過往，正是因為這些年的人生歷練，讓凡寧得以用不同的視角進行觀察、分析，進而勝任採訪工作；初至德國時，因為沒有執照加上歐洲人習慣自己動手佈置居家環境，讓凡寧原有的能力在此看似無用武之地。</p><p data-nodeid=\"4849\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>然而，美感的培養及累積卻內化成獨特的攝影眼，讓她得以用另一種方式，繼續延續她對設計的熱忱。從空間設計師到時尚影像文字工作者，凡寧的人生看似誤打誤撞，或許只是在等待一個對的時機點！</p><p data-nodeid=\"4850\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"4914\" alt=\"凡寧專訪\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/66728da275e58cf0bb403fc4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 700px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></p><p data-nodeid=\"4851\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>這次她特地返台進行攝影教學，僅停留短短數天，她笑說每次回來一天都只睡四、五個小時，很累，卻很幸福，因為沒想過還有機會可以回來台灣、用中文工作。</p><blockquote data-nodeid=\"4852\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 17.5px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 190, 164); border-top-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-right-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><p data-nodeid=\"4853\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.75em;\">「我離開台灣快十六年了，台灣人已經不把我當台灣人，可是對德國人來說，我永遠都是一個外來者。」</p></blockquote><p data-nodeid=\"4854\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>在兩座城市間遊走，總有感到疑惑的時候，若能找到自我價值，便能清楚地知道自己是誰，無須被標籤限制。現在的凡寧眼神中帶有堅毅，或許仍會有迷惘的時刻，但因為有了「攝影」做她的指南針，總會帶她找到回家的方向。</p><p data-nodeid=\"4855\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>＊備註一：在德國若要離婚，必須先跟法院提出離婚申請，雙方分居滿一年後才能進入離婚程序。離婚手續速度與過程依雙方是否達成共識為主，有的可能長達數年。一旦提出離婚分居，雙方可各自發展新的感情結交伴侶。</p>', NULL, 33, 0, '2025-02-17 03:06:34', '2025-02-17 03:06:34');
