(13, 'https://www2.canon.com.hk/myContent/article/10465/images/image001.jpg', 48, NULL, NULL, 2, '無人之境攝影術', NULL, '<p><br></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"http://www2.canon.com.hk/myContent/article/10465/images/image001.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 687px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(111, 111, 111); border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(171, 171, 171); font-size: 13px; padding: 6px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\">EOS 70D &bull; EF-S 18-135mm f/3.5-5.6 IS &bull; f/11 &bull; 60s &bull; ISO 200<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">(with 10 stop ND filer)</div></div><p id=\"isPasted\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\">細看以上的相片，是否覺得既熟識但又陌生？其實這是位於旺角的花園街，是香港最熱鬧的街道之一；陌生是因為在大白天，很難會看到這樣空蕩蕩的花園街，像是整個世界只淨下一片沈寂，充滿超現實的感覺。本文將會為大家介紹怎樣拍出恍如無人之境的街道，大家一起來試試吧！</p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">慢快門配合中性密度濾鏡（或稱減光鏡）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\">有一定攝影經驗的讀者，或許都會猜到這是慢快門攝影的其中一種應用方式。我們往往會透過長時間曝光來留住物件移動的軌跡，如車軌、星流跡等。在慢快門下，行人的動態會變得模糊，只有靜止不動的建築物會被清晰地記錄，想進一步加強這種效果，就要想辦法將拉長曝光時間。首先，我們要使用小光圈及盡可能低的ISO感光度拍攝。由於拍攝時間在白天，更要加上減光鏡輔助才可達到理想的效果。</p><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; display: block; height: 1em; width: 10px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \"Roboto Condensed\", \"Noto Sans\", \"Noto Sans TC\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><br></div><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \"Roboto Condensed\", \"Noto Sans\", \"Noto Sans TC\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" style=\"width: 677px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></div><p style=\"text-align: left;\">減光鏡是濾鏡的一種，作用是可以大幅減少入光量，繼而延長曝光時間，很適合用於拍攝長曝作品。減光鏡的減光級數以ND表示，例如ND-2即是減2級EV值，ND-4即是減4級EV值，如此類推。濾鏡減了多少級EV值，快門就可以減慢多少級，例如本來設定是f/16、ISO 100、1/2s，加上ND-4減光鏡後，快門速度則可以在整體曝光值不變下，減慢至8秒 (1/2s&rarr;8s，減慢了4級)。而是次拍攝的目標，就是要將曝光時間延長至1分鐘或以上，大家可因應實際環境而加配不同級數的減光鏡拍攝。</p><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; display: block; height: 1em; width: 10px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \"Roboto Condensed\", \"Noto Sans\", \"Noto Sans TC\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><br></div><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; max-width: 100%; margin-bottom: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \"Roboto Condensed\", \"Noto Sans\", \"Noto Sans TC\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"http://www2.canon.com.hk/myContent/article/10465/images/image003.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 687px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(111, 111, 111); border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(171, 171, 171); font-size: 13px; padding: 6px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\">EOS 70D &bull; EF-S 18-135mm f/3.5-5.6 IS &bull; f/16 &bull; 120s &bull; ISO 200<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">(with 10 stop ND filer)</div><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\'color: rgb(49, 49, 49); font-family: \"Roboto Condensed\", \"Noto Sans\", \"Noto Sans TC\", sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\' id=\"isPasted\">以慢快門拍攝移動中的行人，只是為了讓他們消失於畫面之中。所以大家應選擇一些人或車不會停留的地點，避免於交通燈位置、觀景台或車站等會有人、車流聚集的地方拍攝，以呈現無人之境的寂靜效果。</span></p></div>', NULL, 36, 0, '2025-02-23 01:42:35', '2025-02-23 01:42:35');
INSERT INTO `article` (`id`, `image_path`, `user_id`, `product_id`, `course_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `subtitle`, `content`, `tag_id`, `like_count`, `is_deleted`, `created_at`, `update_time`) VALUES
(14, 'https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2025/02/20/250220-60984-1.png', 48, NULL, NULL, 1, 'Canon 新款隨身相機 PowerShot V1 發布！動靜皆宜、支援 4K 60p 錄影', NULL, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: var(--textMarginBottom); margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: var(--textFontSize); vertical-align: baseline; line-height: var(--textLineHeight); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 微軟正黑體, 新細明體, sans-serif, Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\" id=\"isPasted\">Canon 今日發布最新款隨身相機&nbsp;PowerShot V1，採用大尺寸的 1.4 吋感光元件，更在小巧機身內塞入風扇，實現 4K 60p 高畫質錄影。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: var(--textMarginBottom); margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: var(--textFontSize); vertical-align: baseline; line-height: var(--textLineHeight); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 微軟正黑體, 新細明體, sans-serif, Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">全新的&nbsp;PowerShot V1 是 Canon 繼 2019 年的 G5 X Mark II、G7 X Mark III 之後，再度發表類單眼相機，僅 426g 重的機身結合了等效焦距約 16-50mm、F2.8-4.5 的光圈鏡頭；採用比 1 吋大上兩倍的 1.4 吋感光元件，相近於 M43 的面積，帶來比傳統 1 吋機型更多的進光量且提供最多 2230 萬像素的解析力。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: var(--textMarginBottom); margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: var(--textFontSize); vertical-align: baseline; line-height: var(--textLineHeight); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 微軟正黑體, 新細明體, sans-serif, Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">PowerShot V1 使用了 Canon 旗下最新的雙像素 CMOS AF 自動對焦技術，能夠偵測移動中的動物或是兒童，透過演算法加以鎖定，輔以最高連拍每秒 30 張，確保照片每張都清晰；內建「進階A+」模式，即便是傳統相機難以拍攝的夜景、逆光畫面，皆能在偵測辨識之後，透過 HDR 等技術來拍下美麗的照片。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: var(--textMarginBottom); margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: var(--textFontSize); vertical-align: baseline; line-height: var(--textLineHeight); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 微軟正黑體, 新細明體, sans-serif, Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">由於定位在&nbsp;PowerShot 系列，這款相機仍舊是以錄影功能為亮點，相機額外安裝散熱風扇，使 4K 30p 錄影時間可以長達兩個多小時，最高可以實現 4K 60p 畫質、4：2：2 10bit 色彩格式；具備物件追蹤能力，可以確保主題保持在畫面的任一位置。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: var(--textMarginBottom); margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: var(--textFontSize); vertical-align: baseline; line-height: var(--textLineHeight); text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: 微軟正黑體, 新細明體, sans-serif, Arial; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Canon PowerShot V1 預計四月下旬在日本上市，售價為 148,500 日圓（約 32,355 元），台灣上市資訊仍待官方公佈</p>', NULL, 125, 0, '2025-02-23 01:50:00', '2025-02-23 01:50:00'),
(15, 'https://media.vogue.com.tw/photos/6793508582ea40ac0d409802/2:3/w_2240,c_limit/W1.jpg', 48, NULL, NULL, 4, '藝術與人的關係－從攝影看見七位新銳創作者', '生命可以在鏡頭前無限延續，在亞洲攝影創作者年度盛會 Wonder Foto Day 開跑之際，邀你一起透過攝影創作，細品生活。', '<p data-nodeid=\"321\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">攝影，是將生活中的細節與風景濃縮於一個框裡，以獨特的光景和手法拼湊心裡的態度、觀念和價值。從鏡頭和畫面裡體悟感受、創造意義，它是藝術與人的親密關係，也是坦然以對的誠實，一種面對自己的敘述方式。</p><p data-nodeid=\"322\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>在藝術裡瞭解攝影，在創作中認識七位傑出的新銳攝影創作者，以不同的形式刻畫對世界的態樣和想望，於是你我對於空間、對於生命力，足以有截然不同的解讀，透過作品的刻畫描繪新的視角可能。</p><p data-nodeid=\"323\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"363\" alt=\"張晏齊作品\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/666fe7afa5fda39db3655f43\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">▲張晏齊作品</p><p data-nodeid=\"324\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>張晏齊，後九零年代的青澀，生處於數位時代的璀璨年華，他說自個兒有些悶騷又帶點幽默，憑藉著天馬行空的姿態，在創作裡除了任意馳騁，卻也不得不將其視為一面鏡，在鏡頭後面的世界裡看見自己，沉著省思，「攝影是一種對自己的反思、對話、不論簡單還是複雜，都是自己走過的痕跡。」</p><p data-nodeid=\"325\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>創作是條漫漫長路，能走的路很遠，但揹著相機的創作者，無論是肉眼或鏡頭，經歷過的畫面都已紮紮實實在心裡活過了一回。</p><p data-nodeid=\"326\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"370\" alt=\"王鼎元作品\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/666fe7bdaebd01a6ec50a144\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">▲王鼎元作品</p><p data-nodeid=\"327\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>王鼎元，道道地地的台北人，因著都市的繁華，看見了速食科技的文化。作品曾多次在攝影圈獲獎，2012 年首次以編導攝影的形式創作《臉上的光彩》，闡述著人們透過手機聯絡感情，卻忘了現實生活中身邊的人，作品不僅獲選為 epson 百人聯展作品，2017 年更再次重新詮釋創作，透過刻意的場景安排與燈光的強調，嘲弄數位時代下人們的悲歌。</p><p data-nodeid=\"328\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>本是立意良善的科技工具，卻成了人際關係中的一道高牆，人們喜悅於手中的小框框，直到所有的笑容，都可以如戲劇般地被完美演繹。</p><p data-nodeid=\"329\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"377\" alt=\"胡小隆作品\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/666fe7cf6fa4990280873896\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">▲胡小隆作品</p><p data-nodeid=\"330\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>不甘於只做藝術家，他還是位小說家，現居上海的攝影創作者胡小隆，以自身經驗擬人地刻畫蛇的靈動與神聖。普遍被認作邪惡與危險的蛇類，在中國古代卻象徵吉祥與神聖，胡小隆以「蛇的視角」探索虛實間的敘事線，思索生命、時間、歸屬感以及自然議題，以同一地點、不同角度與時間的畫面，層層堆疊，搭載多種訊息，生命亦是如此，處在崎嶇的環境裡，更需要柔軟的姿態，如同小蛇一般。</p><p data-nodeid=\"331\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>對胡小隆而言，攝影並不單只是記錄，而是和所有的藝術表現形式一樣，都是一種自我表達，而這樣的表達需要直覺與等待。</p><p data-nodeid=\"332\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"384\" alt=\"FM 作品\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/666fe7d9aebd01a6ec50b73a\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">▲FM 作品</p><p data-nodeid=\"333\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>有著年輕的外表卻細膩的心，創作者 FM 由蘇穎珊及牟珮萱兩人組成，標準青澀的大學新鮮人，很是年輕卻嗅到社會現象，在《Sugar Holic》系列作品中，他們將社會種種的壓力和情緒擬人化、具象化，肉眼看見的糖果與醫療器具，背後藏著的是嗜甜症，生日派對的歡樂中隱隱約約透著歷史背景的荒謬光景，而眼見又真的為憑嗎？</p><p data-nodeid=\"334\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>炫彩奪目是糖果給人的第一印象，而隱藏其中的是更多可能的變調畫面，甜膩中帶點不得不的苦澀，人生或許也如此，當所有人事物都是一體兩面，你選擇看見哪一面？</p><p data-nodeid=\"335\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"391\" alt=\"楊曉東（Tongchar）作品\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/666fe7e63e14cfc85ac2dd8f\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">▲楊曉東（Tongchar）</p><p data-nodeid=\"336\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>生於澳門，在台灣攻讀圖文傳播及數位出版碩士，楊曉東（Tongchar）近年作品泛以兒時記憶、對社會的認知以及情緒為題，他認為攝影術自發明以來，往往被視為一種證據，有如新聞界中的「有圖有真相」，而影像被見證的成功之處，實際上卻是符合了人類與影像與真實間關係的想像。</p><blockquote data-nodeid=\"337\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 17.5px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 190, 164); border-top-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-right-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><p data-nodeid=\"338\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.75em;\">照片只是一種「類比之物」，往往被認為是特定事物的指涉和再現。－羅蘭巴特（符號學家）</p></blockquote><p data-nodeid=\"339\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>觀音兵，一句香港俚語，多用來形容男性為了追求女性，願意為其做各種事情，事事順從，無論對方是否喜歡自己。Sweetheart Soldier 系列作品以一位女性和她的玩偶比喻三角關係，而究竟哪一個才是她所愛，又或者所有都只是一時興起的玩物？彼此間的關係，無從得知。</p><p data-nodeid=\"340\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"399\" alt=\"林旼謙作品\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/666fe7f0a5fda39db3658e15\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">▲林旼謙作品</p><p data-nodeid=\"341\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>我們生處於一個快速的噴射時代，充斥著速食食品、宛如大海的新興資訊以及日益更迭的 3C 產品。當經典遇上流行、古典衝撞現代會是什麼樣的風景？擅長影像編輯、平面設計、攝影的林旼謙，以細緻古典的光線構圖，搭配極為現代的日常物件，營造了錯置與衝突，冀望兩者之間的奇異和連結，可以是時代變革中需要思考的差異之處。</p><p data-nodeid=\"342\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>世代的交錯融合，書寫著時間和那些難以抗拒的明日，它是時代的現象，難掩怪異，卻襯著鏡頭的眼光，交織出真實變化的時代足跡。</p><p data-nodeid=\"343\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"406\" alt=\"倫德爾作品\" src=\"https://images.hahow.in/images/666fe7fd6fa499028087545d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">▲倫德爾作品</p><p data-nodeid=\"344\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>倫德爾，橫跨設計、攝影、插畫、服裝設計與飾品設計等多種領域，創作風格常帶有強烈個人特色和詭譎的獨特感，時而取景於台灣秘境或廢墟，以童年想像或夢境為創作靈感，散發一種謎樣氣息，引人探究之魅力。他的作品從草稿、道具服飾至攝影與後製皆獨力完成，在虛實之間，宛若進入無盡的漩渦，在廢墟中暗藏古典少女，視覺表現令人印象深刻。</p><p data-nodeid=\"345\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>光與影的進入像是一座樂園，讓角色和空間起了化學變化，演繹一場魔幻般的藝術。在攝影微妙的鏡頭框外，不單是作品，攝影創作者更是衝撞既有觀念的想像，創造意外，感受體悟，欲點燃每一個看待事物的新眼光。</p><p data-nodeid=\"346\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>如果你想，攝影可以為你開啟與藝術對話的大門，親自感受，實際觀賞，甚至與創作者面對面交流，擁抱新的感官體驗，下個週末，一起去看展吧！</p>', NULL, 73, 0, '2025-02-23 02:15:39', '2025-02-24 16:48:04'),
(16, 'https://images.hahow.in/images/60f6a63cb355920006a9b450', 34, NULL, NULL, 2, '張道慈親授，三個取景小技巧，體會「減法攝影」中的感官加乘', 'PTT getmarry 版傳說級婚紗攝影師張道慈，這次不是要教你一門，叫做「減法攝影」的技巧，而是要分享一種概念，想要教你怎麼「看」，怎麼拆解眼前的世界。', '<p data-nodeid=\"288\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">相信疫情期間大家都辛苦了，也多了許多再次探訪世界的想像，希望以下三個小方法，能幫助到你下一次拿起手機或相機，擷取時間長河裡的重要影格。</p><h1 data-nodeid=\"289\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 23px; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>多利用「井字型」構圖來幫助自己安排畫面的物體</h1><p data-nodeid=\"290\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>許多人在初學攝影時，遇到濃霧、天候不佳的狀況會選擇收起相機，但其實起了大霧時，更加適合練習構圖，因為大多數的景物都被雲層或濃霧遮蔽，只留下比較靠近自己的物體，於是就可以不斷的嘗試把物體放在不同的區域，試著營造不同的感覺。</p><p data-nodeid=\"291\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>範例一：將兩艘小船，分別安放在左側及右側的 1/3 等分線上，並且都屬於中央的區域，整體畫面就會相當的平衡。</p><p data-nodeid=\"292\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"329\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/60f6a4f9520500000796ba02\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></p><p data-nodeid=\"293\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>範例二：將畫面中的小船，放在中央下方的區塊中，其他地區全部留白，讓人可以對畫面有更多的想像，以及足夠寬廣的延伸感。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"333\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/60f6a51db355920006a9b1b1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></p><h1 data-nodeid=\"294\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 23px; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>幫你的主體找一個單純的「背景」</h1><p data-nodeid=\"295\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>我在新加坡的街上，遠遠的看見了一群八哥在吃桌上的剩菜，於是我一路接近，並且調整拍攝的位置，由於八哥是黑色的,如果將他放在暗色的背景處會很不明顯，而一邊拍照時想到可以利用鮮黃色的椅背來突出八哥，一邊走動一邊拍攝，直到完全把八哥「框」入背景中，同時他也剛好飛走，得到了一張更加有趣的照片。</p><blockquote data-nodeid=\"296\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; font-size: 17.5px; border-left: 5px solid rgb(0, 190, 164); border-top-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-right-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 190, 164); font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><p data-nodeid=\"297\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; line-height: 1.75em;\">無論是拍小動物、拍一棟房子，或是拍人，都可以利用相機的視角，改變拍攝的背景，進而突出主題。</p></blockquote><h6 data-nodeid=\"298\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 16px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><br></h6><h6 data-nodeid=\"299\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 16px; text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"338\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/60f6a55d520500000796ba38\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></h6><h1 data-nodeid=\"300\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 20px 0px 10px; font-size: 23px; font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.5; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87); text-align: left; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>注意「人臉」擺放的位置</h1><p data-nodeid=\"301\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>出門在外，突然拿起相機想幫身邊的朋友拍點照片，如果直接按下快門，很常會因為背景太亂，而讓照片找不到重點。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">選擇單純素色的背景，可以有效地突出人的「側臉」，讓臉上的輪廓清晰後，自然就會從會面中跑出來。</p><p data-nodeid=\"302\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>即便身處複雜的街道，試著找出一塊<strong data-nodeid=\"352\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">乾淨的背景</strong>來擺放你的人物吧。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">如果找不到乾淨的背景怎麼辦？<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">別忘了，天空也可以當作乾淨的背景喔！</p><p data-nodeid=\"303\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65); font-family: \"PingFang TC\", 微軟正黑體, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: transparent; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" data-nodeid=\"354\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://images.api.hahow.in/images/60f6a5d3cd071800075b206f\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; width: 818px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>', NULL, 255, 0, '2025-02-23 20:00:01', '2025-02-23 20:00:01'),
